            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1724339315918-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1724339315918-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Layer some of the <strong>pork</strong> <strong>ragù</strong> over the bottom of an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, then top with some of your <strong>lasagne sheets</strong> (be careful not to overlap the pasta!)</p><p>Repeat this process until you end up with a final layer of lasagne sheets</p><p>Tip: You may need to layer differently depending on the size of your dish!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1649848598202-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1649848598202-x400.jpg",
